d(\theta_1,\theta_2) = \left\{     \begin{array}{ll}         |\theta_1-\theta_2| & \mbox{if } |\theta_1-\theta_2|\le \pi \\         2\pi-|\theta_1-\theta_2| & \mbox{else}     \end{array} \right.
